videos.headline: Questionable flag is thrown after UCLA QB gets obliterated
videos.description: UCLA QB Dorian Thompson-Robinson gets hit hard into sideline equipment, which draws a questionable flag.

videos.headline: Colorado QB fires 57-yard pass to tie game
videos.description: Colorado QB Steven Montez heaves a 57-yard pass to a wide open Laviska Shenault Jr. to tie the game at 7-7.
